---
title: Curried Chicken Stew with Garlic Naan
description: Is there anything better than a big bowl of warm chicken curry? It's a hug from the inside out! Tender chicken, aromatic curry spices and roasted sweet potatoes fill the bowl to the brim! Don't forget to wipe it clean with the garlic naan.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-poulet-au-cari-ac9b7a5d.jpg
